\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11814545 RV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13045969\charrsid8921974 No. No, no, I don't remember - don't remember doing anything like that.
