\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12023959 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13045969\charrsid8921974 Did you ever have a bicycle?
