I think I - we have played netball I think it was but I don't think we had a lot of that when we was at school you know. Don't - I know the blooming teacher - in school once who - she was always fond of smacking you round the face. They're no
t allowed to do that now. But it would be a good job if they did in some - I don't mean smacking you round the face but correcting you - they're not allowed to do it. She was a dabster for that. One - one day - I was - not really mischievious but I could 
s
ee fun and something she was saying to us once when I was listening to her or not I don't know and - she said something to me and I bust out laughing and her face, ever so rude but - I couldn't help it, I had to. And she said I - that was insulting to me.
 It was and I didn't mean it to be did I.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12023959 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13045969\charrsid8921974 You got a fit of giggles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11814545 RV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13045969\charrsid8921974 Yes. 'Cos I could - can always see the funny side of anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12023959 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13045969\charrsid8921974 What happened to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11814545 RV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13045969\charrsid8921974 Oh well, put in the corner. After I said I was sorry - I didn't want to but I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12023959 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13045969\charrsid8921974 You didn't get your face slapped?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11814545 RV  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13045969\charrsid8921974 No, she didn't do it then, no, 'cos she could see that - I didn't mean it afterwards. But she was a terror for things. Very strict.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12023959 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13045969\charrsid8921974 Did you ever go to any concerts or theatres when you were small?
