Only the children - no, no. We had to mar - I remember marching two by two, you know - that was really a magnificent play. I really - those sort of things you remember a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12023959 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13045969\charrsid8921974 Did you ever go to a music hall when you were little?
